The paper focuses on mapping relationships between scientific papers using co-citation methodology, which is commonly used in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social networks (cs.SI). The study also involves categorizing articles according to disciplines and specialties, which could fall under the sub-categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
